name.value: TNM Distant Metastases Category Value Set

description.value: Result values for M category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the M category, according to TNM staging rules.

name.value: TNM Distant Metastases Maximum Value Set

description.value: Values for TNM distant metastases category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMDistantMetastasesCategoryVS.

name.value: TNM Distant Metastases Staging Type Value Set

description.value: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for distant metastases (M) staging observation.

name.value: TNM Primary Tumor Category Value Set

description.value: Result values for T category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the T category, according to TNM staging rules.

name.value: TNM Primary Tumor Maximum Value Set

description.value: Values for TNM primary tumor category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMPrimaryTumorCategoryVS.

name.value: TNM Primary Tumor Staging Type Value Set

description.value: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for primary tumor (T) staging observation.

name.value: TNM Regional Nodes Category Value Set

description.value: Result values for N category. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for the N category, according to TNM staging rules.

name.value: TNM Regional Nodes Maximum Value Set

description.value: Values for TNM regional nodes category must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMRegionalNodesCategoryVS.

name.value: TNM Regional Nodes Staging Type Value Set

description.value: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for regional nodes (N) staging observation.

name.value: TNM Stage Group Maximum Value Set

description.value: Values for TNM stage group must be selected from this value set, which includes all codes from UICC and all codes from TNMStageGroupVS.

name.value: TNM Stage Group Staging Type Value Set

description.value: Identifying codes for the type of cancer staging performed, i.e., clinical, pathological, or other, for the stage group observation.
Result values for cancer stage group using TNM staging. This value set contains SNOMED-CT equivalents of UICC codes for Stage Group, according to TNM staging rules.
